title: Heems : Converse Red Light Sessions:
description:
Himanshu Suri aka Heems, from alternative hip-hop group Das Racist, joined us at Red Light Radio's studio in the heart of Amsterdam's red light district to record the very first of our new live Red Light Sessions. Check it out.

Stay tuned here for more Converse Red Light Sessions
